<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1933939' id='t-1933939'>don't rely on one-sided conversations.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1936419' id='t-1936419'>So that's the idea, I think, worth spreading.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1939568' id='t-1939568'>We have a sign, a badge tab,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1942961' id='t-1942961'>we wear badges at work with lanyards,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1944850' id='t-1944850'>and if I could make a plug,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1946263' id='t-1946263'>my badge lanyard at work says, &quot;Dallas Cowboys.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1949010' id='t-1949010'>Go Dallas.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1952507' id='t-1952507'>I've just alienated half the audience, I know.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1955173' id='t-1955173'>So the lanyard that our people</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1959069' id='t-1959069'>who work in the organization</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1960854' id='t-1960854'>that does our crypto-analytic work</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1963274' id='t-1963274'>have a tab that says, &quot;Look at the data.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1965215' id='t-1965215'>So that's the idea worth spreading.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1966751' id='t-1966751'>Look at the data.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
